name: Cathy
dialogue: "So, Alice, have you ever tried stand-up comedy? I think it would be hilarious!"

name: Alice
dialogue: "Oh, wow, Cathy! I've always wanted to try it out! But I'm a bit too shy to get up in front of a crowd."

name: Cathy
dialogue: "Nonsense, Alice! You're so brave and adventurous. I'm sure you would be great at it!"

name: Alice
dialogue: "Thanks, Cathy. Maybe one day I'll muster up the courage to give it a try."
